SERVER CREATION

creating package.json - npm init

create nodemodules - install express - npm i express

create index.js(main entry point)
  - in index.js
    1)import express
    2)create an appication using express
    3)setup a port number
    4)use jsonparse for server response

integration - 
   1)install cors - npm i cors
   2)import cors into index.js
   3)using cors specify the  origin to the server

services -
create a folder Services - also find 2 files
    1)dataServices.js
    2)db.js

mondodb connection 
     1)install mongoose - npm i mongoose
     2)import mongoose into db.js
     3)define the connection string
     4)create model for products and export it

resoving API calls in index.js
       1)import dataSERVICES

create logic in dataservice
    1)import DB
    2)define function

final step define api call in index.js




